- Use `tonic::transport::Server` for creating gRPC servers
- Implement gRPC clients with `tonic::transport::Channel`
- Use `prost` for Protocol Buffers compilation and integration
- Implement streaming with `tonic::Streaming`
- Use `tonic::Status` for error handling and gRPC status codes